Kya tumhe lagta hai ki tumhare sapne bahut bade hain? Ya rasta bahut mushkil hai? Aksar hume lagta hai ki kismat ne rasta rok rakha hai... lekin sach toh ye hai, ki rasta kismat ne nahi, tumhare darr ne roka hai."
​(10-25s: Building Curiosity)
"Ek baat yaad rakhna... ek chattan ko todne ke liye hamesha ek bade hathode ki zaroorat nahi hoti. Us chattan ko woh paani ki boond bhi tod deti hai jo bar-bar, lagatar ek hi jagah par girti hai. Ise kehte hain Consistency ki taqat."
​(25-45s: Increasing Pace/Energy)
"Duniya tumse kahegi ki tumhare bas ka nahi hai. Tumhare dost tum par hasenge, aur tumhara khud ka dimaag tumhe sau (100) bahane dega rukne ke liye. Lekin wahi wo waqt hota hai jab ek aam insan aur ek 'Legend' ke beech ka farq tay hota hai. Jab thak jao, toh aaram karo... lekin kabhi Haar Mat Maano."
​(45-65s: Powerful & Loud Tone)
"Safalta talent se nahi, roz ki gayi chhoti-chhoti mehnat se milti hai. Roz khud ko 1% behtar banao. Girna bura nahi hai, gir kar wahi pade rehna sabse badi haar hai. Apne 'Kyun' (Why) ko yaad karo... tumne shuru kyun kiya tha? Kya is din ke liye ki tum beech raste se laut jao?"
​(65-80s: Closing - High Motivation)
"Utho! Apne andar ki us aag ko phir se jalao. Aaj ka din tumhara hai. Tab tak mat ruko jab tak tum wahan na pahunch jao jahan pahunchne ka tumne khwab dekha tha. Kyunki yaad rakhna... haarne wala sirf ek bahana dhundta hai, aur jeetne wala sirf ek raasta."
​(80-90s: Final Punchline)
"Faisla tumhara hai. Bahana ya Raasta? Ziddi bano aur kar dikhao. Let's go!"
